<body>
    <h1>Reservation Checked In</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p local-id=3D"f86d2887dbac"><strong>Component type:</strong> Trigg=
er</p>
<p local-id=3D"bee0fdaac4b5"><strong>Category:</strong> Reservations</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"8c0bb0831990" id=3D"ReservationCheckedIn-Overview">Overview=
</h2>
<p local-id=3D"adee7178a3f2">The <strong>Reservation Checked In</strong> tr=
igger fires automatically whenever a guest is checked in to a reservation a=
t your property. It serves as the starting point of a workflow, providing d=
etailed information about the reservation and the associated guest at the m=
oment of check-in.</p>
<p local-id=3D"78d14203d91d">This trigger has no input fields to configure =
=E2=80=94 simply add it to your workflow and it will start listening for ch=
eck-in events. When a guest is checked in, the component outputs all releva=
nt reservation and guest details on the <strong>out</strong> port, which ca=
n then be used by subsequent steps in your workflow.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"d7f678f1-2e17-43ac-be06-4cc9b6c4abde">
<h2 local-id=3D"da70ec9a4596" id=3D"ReservationCheckedIn-InputFields">Input=
 Fields</h2>
<p local-id=3D"c7352c81f821">This component is a trigger and does not have =
any input fields. It activates automatically when a reservation is checked =
in at your property.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"c1f20d5d-2ed7-4588-8929-ef0ee6df4104">
<h2 local-id=3D"e28500ac297a" id=3D"ReservationCheckedIn-OutputFields">Outp=
ut Fields</h2>
<p local-id=3D"91a1b360ef26">When a reservation is checked in, the followin=
g values are available on the <strong>out</strong> output port for use in s=
ubsequent workflow steps:</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"931c360833a0" id=3D"ReservationCheckedIn-ReservationDetails=
">Reservation Details</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"a18153da-f61a-426c-ae65-cd3=
efd3bb646" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"a8b31bcd-14ba-4d9e-bc98-dc0adfa77854">
<th data-local-id=3D"f369672e-332c-404e-a054-5ff519db0703" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
