nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c7be583a9583">The current state of the reservation (e.g., <c=
ode>Started</code>).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8a08d20e-f875-4881-ad5e-9d106b879441">
<td data-local-id=3D"def05d2d-451f-4e08-8c84-ce93ca89194e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"050aa490fcd6"><strong>Origin</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"dcf3f0fc-ba93-4e2c-a4b3-ea9598d605f3" class=3D"conflue=
