nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cb423439e800">Text (GUID)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"5d6bd8a3-f5ce-483b-abfa-d8686eefbe1e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"58a96dcb4926">The unique identifier of the space (room) assi=
gned to the reservation. At the time of check-in, a space is typically assi=
gned.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d356e300-757a-47e7-a236-8bce71b5af63">
