<p local-id=3D"98b358f6786a">Text (GUID)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c8682932-eb1a-4d06-916c-f71aa1c52bd8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"36a02130b643">The unique identifier of the customer who made=
 the booking. This may differ from the guest staying in the room. May be em=
pty if the booker information is not available.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
