<p local-id=3D"da6eb96c7067"><strong>Guest Nationality Code</strong></p></t=
d>
<td data-local-id=3D"7e8a8eee-adcf-45a4-90c6-0363f8ae790a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ff0c2696831a">Text</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f60ff57b-0927-4ae3-848d-255b62eaed93" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"463f1e8c3cd5">The ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 country code representi=
ng the guest's nationality (e.g., <code>US</code>, <code>GB</code>, <code>D=
E</code>). May be empty if not provided.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"6403793f-506d-49eb-a56f-17dbe8f1db23">
<td data-local-id=3D"68e76f4e-06e5-4259-b709-8b0a6d2f5a3b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9c24ebe1884a"><strong>Guest Preferred Language Code</strong>=
</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"392f74ae-b590-400a-9285-868f85d38454" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d0afd7cca521">Text</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e375226f-b879-4f7d-90c6-2af49c85b6da" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7acc4eac5219">The language code representing the guest's pre=
ferred language (e.g., <code>en-US</code>, <code>de-DE</code>). May be empt=
y if not set.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ab540700-9412-496b-9daa-5d4388ecbbbd">
<td data-local-id=3D"4f860c01-4209-4267-b803-a93339e708f6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f63afd1da507"><strong>Guest Loyalty Code</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ed50ba74-7773-488b-ad67-baae8ed757c1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"71f2e76d0d70">Text</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"54918c73-a16b-46da-a35b-c8bb28f69de7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"61ba041c80e9">The loyalty program membership code of the gue=
st. May be empty if the guest is not enrolled in a loyalty program.</p></td=
>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"0064a6e5-b56e-485d-8342-8a9030c0794c">
<td data-local-id=3D"646169f8-f1cb-442e-b876-3fac24c6cbc1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ee367ce883ce"><strong>Guest External Identifier</strong></p>=
</td>
<td data-local-id=3D"12aea684-4f67-4e13-987a-788004c0a95d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2af2ea6165ce">Text</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ac380ed1-365b-4ae0-9adc-b6aab83ad359" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"640f2a3918e7">An external identifier for the guest, typicall=
y used for integration with third-party systems (e.g., a CRM or PMS). May b=
e empty if not set.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
