<p local-id=3D"cb843a5235c3">Date &amp; Time</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7b19d2e1-21d2-4ff7-9505-b590fb6f8128" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"78048829dac3">The date and time when the reservation was con=
firmed, in UTC. May be empty for optional reservations that were not confir=
med before check-in.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4d0105ae-1a66-4ed9-9b5e-67f7cbe5c553">
<td data-local-id=3D"b6c0e960-5ad2-4fd3-8362-569c8c8c52f4" class=3D"conflue=
