<td data-local-id=3D"bd228f1a-107f-46f9-9562-930ed137c31b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1ac13340cdbc">Date &amp; Time</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"56bc81c4-d4d4-4f95-9ac9-dc278d070ceb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4268c1e4532f">The date and time when the reservation was can=
celed, in UTC. Empty for active reservations (which is the expected case at=
 check-in).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"0d400cca-805b-41cf-9c5e-ff86750bed03">
<td data-local-id=3D"5f27779c-e104-4a42-a03f-910c8af26068" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"da8be498d58a"><strong>Started (UTC)</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2f64ec22-19d7-45ed-bd62-a8becb5b872a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3fd040ca5940">Date &amp; Time</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0c4a87a6-5d1e-41ac-8a6b-b338f5288602" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"155c5a2b0787">The date and time when the guest was checked i=
n, in UTC. This field is always populated when this trigger fires, as the c=
heck-in event is what causes the trigger to activate.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"7c34e010-dd84-40ea-b1eb-d30b0e0cde7c">
<td data-local-id=3D"3b56bfb0-4f11-4668-a405-b7c09deae0be" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
